HARBECK v. PUPIN. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. January 12, 1894.) Action by Henry Harbeck against Sarah Katherine Pupin.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and PARKER, JJ.

No opinion. The order will be resettled by reversing, order upon the facts. See 25 N. Y. Supp. 952.
